    "zone_id": "9ccd577b-b5a9-40bc-9011-b54207d822f0",
    "title": "Networking Night | Westover Hills",
    "slug": "networking-night-westover-hills-2b78a9",
    "description": "Looking to grow your network without the pressure of structured activities? Join Network Charlotte at Alchemy Charlotte for a casual, come-as-you-are evening of free networking and great conversations! \nArrival | Join us on the third floor of the Dyestuff Building, to check-in and make a “hello, my name is” sticker. \nAgendaless | Come and go as works for you. Our networking nights have no formal agenda or structured activities. \n\nVenue | Alchemy CoWorking: 2459 Wilkinson Blvd, Charlotte, NC 28208 \nParking | Free parking is available throughout the Dyestuff Building’s lot! \nFood & Drinks | Grab dinner in Westover Hills before networking: \n\nIlios Crafted Greek\nPinky’s Westside Grill\nQue Fresa Taqueria + Bar\nStreetcar Bar + Bites\nTyber Creek Pub\n\n\nAbout Alchemy CoWorking | \nAlchemy is a collaborative workspace designed to help individuals and businesses turn everyday ideas into something extraordinary. More than a shared workspace, Alchemy is an active community of entrepreneurs, creatives, nonprofits, and professionals who value flexibility, connection, and growth. \nWith options ranging from dedicated desks, private offices, and meeting rooms, Alchemy meets partners where they are – and helps them get where they’re going. Whether you work in Charlotte or Gastonia, find your next space today! \nLearn more, explore partnership options, or schedule a tour at alchemycowork.com",
