    "title": "Queen City Social | NoDa's Mill District",
    "slug": "queen-city-social-noda-s-mill-district-4c458f",
    "description": "Swap the small talk for real conversation. Join Filled Cups and Network Charlotte, two local communities teaming up to make it easier for adults to make friends and build genuine connections, for a Queen City Social! \nThis event is not about business cards or elevator pitches – it’s about enjoying good company and connection. \nArrival | Join us in UDM’s Food Hall to make a “hello, my name is” sticker! \nNo Agenda, Just Connections | This event is intentionally unstructured, with no formal programming or assigned activities. We keep things open and flexible so you can mingle, chat, and make connections organically throughout the evening. \n\nVenue | Urban District Market (UDM): 2315 N Davidson St, Charlotte, NC 28205 \nParking | Both street and on-site parking are available around UDM! \nPublic Transit | The nearest light rail stop – 25th Street Station – is a ~10 minute walk from UDM \nTo find your most convenient bus route, please visit CATS’s Bus Routes and Schedules page \nFood & Drinks | Enjoy UDM’s 10+ restaurant stalls: \n\nHand Chop Burger Company\nMo:Mo Pasal\nEl Dorado Latin Grill\nPasuta \nKaUdon\nand more!",
